{"tid":891676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老翁拐杖狂敲乘客腳迫讓座　罵「累是你的事」　大叔拒讓一句回絕","createTime":"2018-11-06T10:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:14:08.000Z","uid":212399,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eec8c0ce257c587232afb1405456adefa16326c6","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:15:28.000Z","msg":"「關愛座」或「博愛座」的出現，令讓座由「美德」變成「壓力」。有台灣女網民在facebook發文，指「雖然很多有需要的人是老人，但博愛座不是老人座」，原來她日前目擊了台北捷運上，一名老翁以拐杖狂敲男乘客的腳，並喝斥對方馬上讓座，雖然對方解釋自己剛剛行完山，實在疲倦，惟老翁扔咄咄逼人，說：「爬山是你自己要爬的，關我什麼事？」男子忍無可忍，霸氣回道：「法律有規定博愛座是給老人坐的嗎？沒有，我為什麼不能坐。」令老翁當場無言以對。女網民事後概嘆，不理解為何讓座已「變成老人霸凌乘客的工具」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2056424/org/a5dcf9a1fc479c8828e2f5fb9d2ab0b7.jpg/wfWil2Y2ErqhwpzB8axt0E610kDniHFuiKFCdIihQnQ?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2056424%2Forg%2Fa5dcf9a1fc479c8828e2f5fb9d2ab0b7.jpg%2FwfWil2Y2ErqhwpzB8axt0E610kDniHFuiKFCdIihQnQ%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=c018c073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣有老翁為迫使男乘客讓座，竟用拐杖敲對方的腿。<br />\n女網民日前在facebook群組「爆怨公社」稱，她在上班途中，遇到有老翁甫上捷運便不斷用拐杖敲一名男乘客的腿，要求對方讓出博愛座，並指「博愛座就是給老人坐的，你坐在這裡對嗎？」該名正睡著的男乘客被吵醒後，心情明顯很差，回道：「博愛座是給有需要的人坐，我剛爬山回來真的很累，為什麼不能坐？」<br />\n兩人於是吵了起來，老翁更大聲喝斥男乘客：「爬山是你自己要爬的，關我什麼事？爬山會累就不要爬，坐什麼博愛座。」男乘客亦不甘示弱，憤怒反問：「法律有規定博愛座是給老人坐的嗎？沒有，我為什麼不能坐。」老翁當場無言以對，但仍大聲徑自抱怨，即使有其他乘客願意讓座，但老翁仍不收口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2056445/org/33697144fa0e197d495c5996ad785ef4.jpg/ayirThCkTSW8RfqWbuYeYNkDbUzuackV6YoHqumKB6o?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2056445%2Forg%2F33697144fa0e197d495c5996ad785ef4.jpg%2FayirThCkTSW8RfqWbuYeYNkDbUzuackV6YoHqumKB6o%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=7c5624fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目擊事件經過的女網民表示，涉事老翁甫上捷運便不斷用拐杖敲一名男乘客的腿，指責對方不應坐博愛座。<br />\n女網民直言不滿老翁的態度，甚至想加入罵戰，對老人說「老也是你自己要老的，關捷運乘客什麼事」，惟最終因為不想招惹老翁，於是沈默，又感嘆不理解為何「體諒他人讓位的美德變成老人霸凌乘客的工具」，批評老翁這種擺明「我老這個位置就是我的」的態度毫不尊重他人，又形容他罵人的聲量及「活力度」，「應該可以再活100年，說實話判斷不出這個老人需要被讓座」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2056435/org/6783e0e579b69a538d6700cec340d30c.jpg/zO8SytQk07YVJ8tl1BziaX6ric3hdFuUu7pdDru6XQ4?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2056435%2Forg%2F6783e0e579b69a538d6700cec340d30c.jpg%2FzO8SytQk07YVJ8tl1BziaX6ric3hdFuUu7pdDru6XQ4%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=2af6b628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是次讓座事件引發台灣網民討論應否取消博愛座，並貼出「博愛座人人可坐」海報示意該座位不是只有老人可坐。<br />\n事件曝光後，不少網民也表示看不過眼老翁的行為，稱如果他「好聲好氣」相求，事情就簡單得多。有人亦建議「應該取消博愛座這種讓人倚老賣老的告示」，指博愛座已變成「大風吹搶椅子的遊戲」，人人傷痕累累又得不到該有用意。"},{"pid":"0651783339a1ed2a35bb73e2928b2a03a308104a","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db57efaded4aba5059d2ad42b7d869e5b0e1fd0","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5379c95225207de2273b9fdbb3272eeb2309bf","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19444f13f00bf4c2c87383ff54c3077a7b98f336","tid":891676,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"有心讓，到處都係關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撚早要取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5375123d34b8f225a75ad7f560250502579a4f17","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93de9ff3763fc8d6b6d46afda33e900a60876d7","tid":891676,"uid":4574,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"台灣專做<br />\n呢啲多撚餘嘅嘢<br />\n美其名 人情味<br />\n<br />\n香港班濕鳩無腦 管理層<br />\n仲想學堆一份"},{"pid":"68d0eaa90f5f40b8470719173464f979cc0f067e","tid":891676,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19444f13f00bf4c2c87383ff54c3077a7b98f336","tid":891676,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"有心讓，到處都係關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撚早要取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"以前無set呢樣野 都無咁多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f05eb2d06cf6cb2408c1f469c7f47332ba2d65d","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdac4a613fcd08ecb39c103bfd3e48e68b0090d","tid":891676,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7847cc6933e446edb2d5b443cdc7008412d357","tid":891676,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今朝輕鐵讓完座越諗條氣越唔順<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bJkfkS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bJkfkS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打學佢噉就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f154b00a762a299d73dd22b0e90177f3137a3148","tid":891676,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a93de9ff3763fc8d6b6d46afda33e900a60876d7","tid":891676,"uid":4574,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"台灣專做<br />\n呢啲多撚餘嘅嘢<br />\n美其名 人情味<br />\n<br />\n香港班濕鳩無腦 管理層<br />\n仲想學堆一份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"港台一齊踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da976cded27a49c54792ee571f3dd643a6b480f1","tid":891676,"u